    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-10-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-10-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="56"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d56">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Inquiry files</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Dr. <persName corresp="#p_MSE1" type="from">S. E.
                            Mezes</persName> to the Treasurer of the Inquiry</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_MDH1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Miller</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-10-15">October 15,
                            1918</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. <persName corresp="#p_MDH1">Miller</persName>
                    </hi>: After an official conference <persName corresp="#p_HCEM1">Colonel
                        House</persName> has given instructions that the work of the Inquiry should
                    be speeded up and has authorized a monthly expenditure for this and subsequent
                    months for the Inquiry proper of $25,000 if necessary, with the understanding
                    that additional employees shall be taken on only until the time when the
                    official force proceeds to the Conference, except in such cases as it may prove
                    quite impossible to obtain satisfactory appointees without offering them a
                    longer term.</p>
                <p>Very truly yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_MSE1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">S. E. Mezes</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
